               <text>
                  <paragraph>Ferric subsulfate 259mg/g [0.0638gm Fe <sup>3+</sup>/<sub>ml</sub>]. Preserved with benzalkonium chloride 0.005%. Povidone USP 23.2%. Glycerin USP 13.3%. Purified Water USP.</paragraph>
